Detailed Description

Lists all the accessories available on this mobile phone.

The instance will be Initialized during OnPowerUp(), called by the SubSystemManager(), because the SubSystem constructor will register itself with the SubSystemManager.

BOOLEAN AudioAccessoryStore::UseAccessory (  AudioAccessoryDetails *  accessory  ) 
 

Replace an already registered object with the one passed through the parameter

Parameters:
accessory The new accessory to be used
Returns:
TRUE if the accessory has been replaced.
Note:
The function if the accessory ID provided as parameter already exists in the list. If not, then the function will return FALSE, otherwise the accessory will be replaced. This function is used to avoid dependencies with modules such us BT. In case a derived accessory object has to be used then this function shall be used to "plug in" the new class type
